IMPORTANT: This update will sign you out of Google Drive. You will need to sign back in after updating. Improved support for Google Drive. Improved subscription management. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
Improved support for position markers in WAV files. Improved support for SFTP. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Improved the sorting order of search results. Fixed the display of sent and due indicators. Added additional options for FTP and WebDAV servers. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Support for iOS 15 and watchOS 8. Improved the transcription process. Hear VoiceOver through a headset while recording from the internal mic. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Added a button to skip forward IAP . Added the option to adjust the speed of saved audio IAP . Fixed problem with auto splitting. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Faster app startup 0.52 seconds faster on iPhone 6 . Fixed problem with auto send. Fixed problem when changing the recording quality. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
Fixed problem with auto splitting. Memos in the trash can are now deleted after 30 days. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Automatic transcription of memos. Use a widget to quickly start recording. Stereo recording using the builtin microphones². Directly view progress of downloads uploads and compressions. Rename memos on Apple Watch. Add position markers while recording on Apple Watch¹. Memos are compressed while recording. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update. ¹ Requires an active subscription. ² Requires a compatible device and an active Pro subscription.

Send memos by email without size restrictions except the ones from email providers . Improved connections with https: imesart.com connect.php. More space for list of memos on iPad. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
Fixes login to OneDrive under iOS 13. Introduces an optional subscription. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
Send memos with iMessage. Fixed audio selection slider. Fixed appearance of selection toolbar. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
Support for Dark Mode iOS 13 . Swipe down to dismiss views iOS 13 . Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Encrypt memos sent to cloud services IAP . Faster app startup. Fixed quality issues when playing back to some Bluetooth devices. Fixed use of complications on some Series 2 and 3 watches. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Added support for sending to SharePoint IAP . Fixed connection problems with OneDrive. Fixed upload problem with some WebDAV servers. Fixed reconnection problem with SFTP servers. Added support for all complications of Apple Watch Series 4. Added background recording under watchOS 5. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Encrypt memos sent by email IAP . Improved support of Bluetooth and AirPlay devices. Improved remote control from Apple Watch. Copy a memo by making a long press on it in the list of memos. Fixed crash that stopped recording for some users under iOS 11. Record button is once again easily accessible with VoiceOver. Added support for Drag and Drop. Fixed Pause Play button on lock screen. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Fixes random crash shortly after playback stopped under iOS 11. Much faster to start playing or recording under iOS 11. Fixed a bug that prevented playback until the app restarted. Memos made under watchOS 4 now sync correctly. Buttons in toolbars now work correctly under iOS 11. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
Fixes problem when auto deleting memo. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.

Improved deletion speed when deleting many memos. Fixed linking with Google Drive. Uploads to Dropbox can now exceed 150MB. Many other improvements. Leave us a review on the App Store to tell us what you think about this update.
